Updates Include: 
-Radar Overlay
-fixed shadows
-fixed textures
-more optimization
-Much Brighter.

Gg_oldtimerscorner
============
The objective was to create a fast-paced gun game map, with high fps and is visually appealing.
============
Focused around a old street theme. One large building separates the map, and the combat zone is in a small market plaza. Smaller homes litter the outside. Smoke rises from the chimneys and birds chirp in the distance.
============
32slot, soundscape. Enjoy and provide serious and constructive feedback. Thanks to cheebs for Radar Overlay.
============
After clicking the download button, i would appreciate you assessing / commenting on my map.
